property.value: function onReceiveOSC(message, connections) local argument = message[2][1].value if argument then self.values["text"] = "-" else self.values["text"] = "+" end end

local delay = 500 local last = 0 local flash = false local count = 0 local red
function update() if flash then if count < 10 then local now = getMillis() if(now - last > delay) then count = count + 1 last = now if self.properties.textColor == red then self.properties.textColor = Color(1,1,1,1) else self.properties.textColor = Color(1,0,0,1) red = self.properties.textColor end end else flash = false count = 0 end end end
function onReceiveOSC(message, connections) local argument = message[2][1].value if argument ~= self.values["text"] then if argument == "" then self.values["text"] = "Timecode Monitor" else self.values["text"] = argument flash = true end end end
